Apache-Server
Mysql-database

Query

1)DDL => create,alter,drop,truncate,rename

->create[you can create new things]
  database
  table

->alter[you can modify existing col]
  ->add col
  ->add col after col
  ->datatype change
  ->rename field
  ->drop col

->rename[you can directly rename your table]

->drop[you can drop table]

->truncate[you can clear your entered data but structure will be as it is]


2)DML => [insert,update,delete]
->insert [insert new record]
  ->single value insert
  ->multiple value insert

->update[update the record]
  ->single update value

->delete[delete the record]

3)DQL => [select]

->select all

->select row

->select col

->order wise

4)DCL =>[rollback,commit]


JOIN=>
JOIN[INNER JOIN]
LEFT JOIN
RIGHT JOIN





  
